

Requirements

xdim needs openssl >0.9.8, recommended is >1.0.1r. It is recommended
to use GNU gcc (g++) 4.8 or newer to compile the source. 

Installation

To install xdkim run:
  $ ./configure
  $ make
  $ make install

Now you should have xdkim in /usr/local/bin and xdkim.8 in
/usr/local/man[/man8].

xdkim was tested on
  - Gentoo linux
  - Debian 7 "Wheezy"
  - openSuSE 13.2
  - FreeBSD 10.2

